      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu tapſi bes Prahta\npahr to Redſechanu / ko tawas\nAzis redſehs."
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS fittihs tew\nar tauneem Tuhkumeem/ pee Zet-\nſeem un Jkreem/kas ne warr dſee-\ndinati tapt / no tawas Behdas\nlihdstawas Galwas Wirſum."
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS noweddihs\ntew ar taiwu Rehnizu/ ko tu pahr\ntew eezelfi / us tahdu Tantu/ ko\ntu ne effi paſinnis/neds tawi Teh-\nwi/ un tur kalpoſi tu zitteem Dee-\nweim/ Kohſain un Akmiſaim."
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu buhſi par Breefini-\nbu/un par weenu ſakkanu Wahṛ-\ndu/un par fineekla Wallohu ſtarp\nwiſſeem Landin / us kurren tew\ntas KUNGS atedſihs."
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu isneſiti dauds Schklas\nus Tihrumu/ bet tu maſſafrakſti/\njo tee Siffeni apehdihs to."
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu dehſtifi Wihna-Dahr-\nfus / un apſtrahdaſi tohs / bet\nWihnu tu ne dſerſi nedś falaffiſi/\njo tee Tahripi wiſſu no-ehdihs."
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tew buhſ Etjes-Kohki\nwiſſas tawas Rohbeschäs / bet ar\nEtji tu ne ſwaidifees / jo taws\nEtjes-Kohks taps iſplehſts."
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu dſemdinafi Dehlus un\nMeitas/ bet teem ne buhſ preekſch\ntew buht / jo tee taps Zeetuma\natswesti."
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſi tawi Kohki/un wiſſi\ntawi SemmesAugti paliks Tahri-\npeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Swechineeks/ kaſta-"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch tew aisdoḥs / bet\ntu wiꞥſam ne aisdoḥſt / wiꞥſch\nbuhs par Galwu / bet tu buhſi\npar Astu."
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſas ſchihs Nolahde-\nſchanas nahks pahr tew/ un wa-\njahs tew/ un uſees tew / famehr\ntu iſdeldehts tohpi/ tapehz ka tu\nta KUNGA tawa Deewa Balk-\nfnei ne effi klaufijs / turredams\nwiꞥſa Baufius / un wiꞥſa Lie-\nkumus / ko wiꞥſch tew pawehlejs\nirr."
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee buhſ ſtarp tew pa-\nweenn Siḫni un par weent\nBrihnumu/ ir ſtarp tawu Dsim-\nmunu muhſcham."
    },
    {
      "n": 47,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tai Weeta / ka tu tai-\nKUNGAM tawam Deewam n\neffi kalpojs ar Precku/ un tawa\nSirds Labbumu / ka tew wiﬀa-\nLeetus pahri un pahri bija."
    },
    {
      "n": 48,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad buhſ tew tarveem E-\nnaidneekſeem / ko tas KUNG-\nſtarp tew fuhtihs eeſch Badd\nun Twihſchanas/ un Plikkuma\nun wiſſu Leetu Trubkuma ka-\npoht/ un wiꞥſch liſs weenu Oſe-\nses Juhgii us tawu Kaklu/kame-\nwiꞥſch tew iſdelde."
    },
    {
      "n": 49,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS weddi-\npahr tew weenu Tantu no tah-\nnes/ no tahs Senmes Galla/\ntin ka weensEhrqſis ſcreen/wee-\nTantu / ka Wallohu tu ne prob"
    },
